21:02.796 --> 21:04.764
I enjoyed that.

21:36.329 --> 21:40.832
Last night in Glasgow I had

21:40.833 --> 21:42.734
enough with the deeper issues.

21:42.735 --> 21:44.336
Now I want to go no deeper than

21:44.337 --> 21:52.337
the bottom of a bubbling
calduron of haggis.

21:53.846 --> 21:55.881
A happy place from my past where

21:55.882 --> 21:58.350
once I frolicked young and

21:58.351 --> 22:01.620
carefree in the field
of fried arts.

22:01.621 --> 22:06.958
The university cafe where I
learned at the foot of the

22:06.959 --> 22:10.629
masters the Dao of hot
fat and crispy batter.

22:10.630 --> 22:13.932
Yes, they do a deep-fried Mars

22:13.933 --> 22:15.634
bar and deep-fried pizza.

